          "text": "SLB - Formerly Schlumberger"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "SLB (formerly known as Schlumberger) is a global technology company that leads innovation in the energy industry. They are headquartered in Houston, Texas. They operate in more than 100 countries, with an annual revenue of $36.07 billion, providing cutting-edge solutions to customers across the oil and gas, geothermal, carbon capture, and renewable energy sectors. They are committed to pioneering technological advancements to address the complex energy challenges globally."
        },
