    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "THE PROBLEM"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Fragmented Data and Manual Reporting Bottlenecks"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The Oil Field Marketplace (OFMP) team at SLB saw itself at the crossroads of being unable to utilize operational data effectively. Data from Azure SQL Database and Google Analytics was siloed and demanded manual work for extraction and reporting. This continued dependence on the technical teams and DBAs to satisfy reporting needs created bottlenecks in the following areas:"
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "GET A FREE DATA CONSULTATION",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Delayed data access slowed down managers in analyzing the data needed for critical business decisions"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Lack of tools made non-technical teams unable to generate their own reports"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual data extraction posed the constant risk of errors and discrepancies across reports"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inability to consolidate data from multiple sources to oversee a holistic business performance"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Inefficient utilization of technical resources as they were constantly distracted by routine data extraction tasks from the DBAs"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
