    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "OUR SOLUTION"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "An End-To-End Automated Data Reporting Platform"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 partnered with SLB to design and implement an Azure-powered data ingestion and reporting solution:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Automated Data Ingestion and Transformation"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Utilizing Microsoft Azure’s data services (Azure Data Factory and Azure Databricks) to upgrade manual data consolidation to efficient data ingestion from Azure SQL Database and Google Analytics, and improving data quality, respectively."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Centralized Data Lake"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Serving as a central repository for all raw and processed data, laying down a secure and scalable foundation."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Unified Visualization & Reporting Using Power BI"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Delineating complex operational data in interactive dashboards and reports using Power BI. This was made accessible through the OFMP portal."
        }
      ],
